Is the New Lumi Matte Foundation by Maybelline really worth it? 🤔
As I blindly bought this online, my foundation is not the perfect shade match! I have olive undertones and 115 isn’t quite the right shade for me. Today, I swatched shade 128 at the pop-up store and it looked nice! So definitely know your color match first!
But other than that, it’s really a great formula for the dry and normal skintype. It reminds me a lot of the Armani Luminous Silk Foundation 👀 It’s definitely worth a try if you like hydrating foundations 💦
Stay tuned to find out if this new foundation really is water, sweat & transferproof!
#newfoundation #newfoundationalert #maybellinelumimatte #topnewproducts
